snippet.title: Project Nosferatu - Trailer & Release Date
snippet.description:
Project Nosferatu is a fast-paced Action RPG with a fully customizable arsenal combo battle system. Varied landscapes of an interconnected world bring unique dangers in each area, which tie together a complex story about the mystery of the nocturnal, subterranean species known as "Umbrakhs."

AVAILABLE NOW, on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2279870/Project_Nosferatu/

https://cartelinteractive.co/ for more pictures and info.
